lead_paragraph: Lashann Higgs scored 14 points and Kelsey Lang and Joyner Holmes each added 12 sending No. 14-ranked Texas past Northwestern State 86-39 on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Texas Routs Northwestern St. 86-39 Behind Higgs
